# HTML cache: by default ignored (full coverage runs ~50-80 MB).
# Exceptions: fixture-clinic caches needed by smoke tests + sentral
# prislister + the HelseSmart fixture page. Keeping these committed
# preserves smoke-test determinism without bloating the repo.
data/html_cache/**
